{
  "texts": [
    "• Leveraging Trusted Networks via WhatsApp Groups: We cultivated fruitful collaborations with faculty members and research coordinators at several universities.",
    "Through their established WhatsApp groups for researchers, we disseminated study information, capitalizing on trusted personal networks within academic communities.",
    "Dissemination through Established Email Channels• Collaboration with University Mailing Lists: We secured permission from multiple universities to send concise email invitations to their faculty and research staff listservs.",
    "This approach broadened our reach, guaranteeing inclusivity of researchers from diverse departments and institutions.Participant responses were recorded consecutively until the desired sample size was attained.",
    "Study ToolWe employed a self-administered, pre-designed questionnaire hosted on Google Forms to gather data."
  ]
}